Yes, It can be possible, use @Query annotation before the method in repository and write sql script.
for example:

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-java --&gt;

    @Query(&quot;SELECT u FROM User u WHERE u.status = 1&quot;)
    List&lt;User&gt; findAllActiveUsers();

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

